**********************************
Setup of OCP on RHV 4.3 using Satellite, FreeIPA etc.
**********************************

Prereqs:

To use ovirt:
  dnf install ovirt-engine-cli
  dnf install libovirt{,-devel}
  dnf install python3-devel 
  dnf install gcc libcurl-devel libxml2-devel ruby-devel
  dnf install python3-pycurl

  pip3 install ovirt-engine-sdk-python
  pip3 install curl-config
  pip3 --upgrade ansible --user ????

  Remove any local version of pycurl

To use Kerberos
  pip3 install urllib_gssapi --system


